model_runs.name: stg_customers
model_runs.compiled_code:
SELECT customer_id
  , raw_data->>'customer_name' AS customer_name
  , raw_data->>'tax_id' AS tax_id
  , raw_data->>'state' AS state
  , raw_data->>'city' AS city
  , raw_data->>'loyalty_segment' AS loyalty_segment
FROM "elementary"."elementary"."customers"

model_runs.name: customers
model_runs.compiled_code:
WITH customers AS (
    select
        customer_id,
        valid_from,
        raw_data,
        source_filename,
        loaded_at
    from "elementary"."elementary"."vw_customers"
)

select *
from customers

model_runs.name: vw_customers
model_runs.compiled_code:
WITH vw_customers AS (
    select
        CAST(customer_id AS INT) AS customer_id,
        CAST(TO_TIMESTAMP(valid_from) AS DATE) AS valid_from,
        data::jsonb AS raw_data,
        CAST(source_filename AS VARCHAR) AS source_filename,
        CAST(loaded_at AS TIMESTAMP) AS loaded_at
    from "elementary"."elementary"."customers_raw"
)

select *
from vw_customers
